        "creation_date": 1515765461,
        "body": "<p>You have to cache the cold sequence and reuse it somehow:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Completable c = prepareCompletable()\n\nc.doOnComplete(() -&gt; Log.d(\"OkHttp\", \"done 1\"))\n    .subscribe();\n\nc.doOnComplete(() -&gt; Log.d(\"OkHttp\", \"done 2\"))\n    .subscribe();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>But note that if the first response is fast, you'd still get double calls.<\/p>\n",
